subject: Urgent: Action Required to Prevent Account Suspension
body:
Dear Valued Customer,

We have detected suspicious activity on your account that requires immediate attention. To protect your account, we have temporarily limited access until you verify your identity. If you do not verify your account within 24 hours, your account will be suspended.

Please follow the link below to verify your account information:

Verify your account now: https://securelogin-alerts.com/verify

For your security, failure to complete this verification will result in the permanent suspension of your account.

Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.

Sincerely,
The Support Team
https://securelogin-alerts.com

subject: Project Update and Next Steps
body:
Hi John,
I wanted to give you a quick update on the XYZ project. We’ve completed the initial design phase, and the team is now working on the wireframes. You can view the latest version here:http://company.com/project/xyz-wireframes
Let me know if you have any feedback or if you'd like to schedule a quick call to go over the details. We’re aiming to finalize the designs by the end of the week, so your input would be helpful before we move to the next phase. You can also book a time for our meeting using this link:http://calendly.com/janedoe/meeting
Thanks,Jane

subject: Weekend Plans?
body:
Hey David,
Hope you’re doing well! I was wondering if you have any plans this weekend. A few of us are thinking about going hiking at Green Valley on Saturday morning. It would be great if you could join us!
We’re planning to meet at the trailhead around 8 AM and maybe grab lunch afterward. Let me know if you’re interested or if you have any other suggestions for the weekend.
Talk soon,Emma
